# Auth0 OAuth2 (MCP clients only). Leave blank to run in legacy API-key mode.
# MCP_BASE_URL: public base URL of this MCP server (used as OAuth "resource"/audience).
# AUTH0_ISSUER: Auth0 tenant issuer - keep the trailing slash (matches token `iss`).
# AUTH0_AUDIENCE: Auth0 API Identifier (must equal the access-token `aud`).
# TG_MCP_INTERNAL_SECRET: shared secret for the TG internal user-lookup endpoint.
